# Project Structure

This is a Next.js 15 application with React 19, TypeScript, and Tailwind CSS.

## Key Directories

- [app/](mdc:app) - The main application directory using Next.js App Router
  - [app/page.tsx](mdc:app/page.tsx) - The homepage component
  - [app/layout.tsx](mdc:app/layout.tsx) - The root layout component
  - [app/globals.css](mdc:app/globals.css) - Global CSS styles

- [components/](mdc:components) - Reusable UI components
  - [components/ui/](mdc:components/ui) - UI component library 
  - [components/ui/button.tsx](mdc:components/ui/button.tsx) - Button component

- [lib/](mdc:lib) - Utility functions and shared code
  - [lib/utils.ts](mdc:lib/utils.ts) - Common utility functions

- [public/](mdc:public) - Static assets

## Configuration Files

- [package.json](mdc:package.json) - Project dependencies and scripts
- [next.config.ts](mdc:next.config.ts) - Next.js configuration
- [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json) - TypeScript configuration
- [components.json](mdc:components.json) - UI component configuration
